INSERT INTO [dbo].[BudgetProjects] ([ProjectID], [CategoryID], [ProjectCode], [ProjectName], [CopyDescriptionToNewAFE], [ProjectDescription]) VALUES (351, 3, N'W068', N'W068 - 28" Pipe Replacement', 0, N'28-inch pipe is not readily available in the market.  Our pipe inventory at Greenville is to accomodate Explorer''s longest river crossing on the 28-inch (South Canadian River - 2,600 feet) and some available pipe for repairs and relocation projects.  The stock has depleted to approximately 1,300 ft and requires approximately 3,700 ft. to be replenished to adequate quantity - 4,000 ft.')
