INSERT INTO [dbo].[BudgetProjects] ([ProjectID], [CategoryID], [ProjectCode], [ProjectName], [CopyDescriptionToNewAFE], [ProjectDescription]) VALUES (360, 3, N'W070', N'W070 - VFD Small Parts', 0, N'Purchase spare parts that are needed at the 12 VFD stations.')
